Press any key to continue . . .

Go into client.java and hit “CTRL + G” and type 3203.

That takes you to line 3203, which is where it’s at. The expression starts with “,” which it can’t start with.

If you dunno how to fix it, copy and paste it here so i can have a look at it for you.
